{
  "stem": "27770.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] destroyed the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They had stuff to blow it up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they started to take a fight with the Germans, because they knew what is waiting for them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, this particular place was in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Birkenau, between Birkenau and Auschwitz was 12 kilometer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And by the time was not enough SS to take care of these guys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "By the time they came from Auschwitz, help SS for this SS in Birkenau, they killed 22 SS.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Half of them got killed outside from the-- those 500 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they say about one third, or half, was in the burning crematorium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were singing 'Hatikvah'.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Was a Thursday afternoon, even the sky was bringing them together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You know, it's a sad day, but I will never forget in my life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They say that one or two guys run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I cannot believe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The way Birkenau was organized, wires and wires.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But they say yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you if this is true or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So that's what happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Now, what happened later, later on came [INAUDIBLE] transport came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And was no more crematorium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And from this day, this date on, until January 17, all the older people who arrived at the transport, they stayed alive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "That's what they accomplished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They didn't accomplish days to survive, but they accomplished a nice few hundred people who-- older people who survived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It also could be that the German special let them alive because when the Russia now coming and the world should see that they left older people alive, this could be also because, I mean, they could destroy them in a different way.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They destroyed all the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "None of them was left.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
